&ldquo;After throwing myself to the magma, the being that appeared from there was none other than the one that corrodes everything, &ldquo;the Legendary Dragon.&rdquo;

Just as all the honest hard work she&rsquo;d put in from a young age was about to bear fruit by obtaining the position of fiance to the Crown Prince, it was none other than the willfulness of her younger sister that forced the engagement to be broken for the Duke&rsquo;s older noble daughter, Eliana. Heartbroken, she announced her candidacy to become the &ldquo;Dragon&rsquo;s Bride,&rdquo; an honorable sacrifice, but after she threw herself to the boiling magma below, when awoke she found herself collapsed, covered in drool in a crater and&hellip;?! &ldquo;In accordance with that custom and stuff, I shall marry you!&rdquo;

A turbulent master and servant (?) relationship between &ldquo;the Legendary Dragon&rdquo; Greed, and &ldquo;the Super High Class Lady&rdquo; Eliana, the curtain on their daily lives opens here!

She was the Queen of Song, but she died during her greatest years.
After she was reincarnated, she became a simple trainee. She lost her former glory? It doesn't matter&mdash;no one can compete with her beautiful singer's voice. She's mocked for her lowly birth? It doesn't matter&mdash;her true identity is enough to make the whole world tremble. She owes huge debts? It doesn't matter...
A powerful boss whispered to her: &quot;The debt will disappear if you would become my woman.&quot;
But she is proud: &quot;I'm sorry. I would sell my art, but not my whole self.&quot;
&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;
This is the story of the Queen of Song, of her return to the peak... and an overbearing chairman.

A trap lying on the internet&hellip;
An outcome exceeding expectations&hellip;
This can't be dismissed as being irrelevant to you!

Kyouichirou Oike is a senior high schooler who&rsquo;s most recognizable traits are his slowness and laziness. However, he has another identity: a genius kid who solves the most mysterious and perplexing cases! As he develops a newfound relationship with his bubbly, bold classmate Kotomi Otokuni, due to her meddlin, he gets sucked into the case&hellip;

Can Kyouichirou save Otokuni, who&rsquo;s unable to understand the predicament she&rsquo;s in?!

Hijiri Kaisei, an Alpha, has issues getting close to omegas because he feels guilty over a traumatic incident from his past. Then one day, his senpai tricked him into going to a male omega brothel.

While there, he meets Ryuji, a bitchy maso boy, who is surprisingly different from the other omegas Kaisei met in the past. Will this encounter throw Kaisei into an even darker abyss..?!

&quot;The animal's burning desire&quot;

In a dilapidated castle, Astaroth awoke as a Demon King. With his &lsquo;wisdom from his past life,&rsquo; he would rule over his lands as a thorough &lsquo;realist.&rsquo;

&ldquo;Demon King, why are you attacking the level 1 Heroes?&rdquo;
&ldquo;Defeat them before they become stronger. That is called strategy.&rdquo;

&ldquo;Demon King, why are you sending fake money to the enemy country?&rdquo;
&ldquo;To bring chaos to their economy so they will self-destruct.&rdquo;

&ldquo;The werewolf troops have attacked. Should we use silver bullets?&rdquo;
&ldquo;Not bullets, shoot them with cannons.&rdquo;

And like that, Astaroth &lsquo;reformed&rsquo; the old tendencies. He became a lord who was loved by the people and his subordinates, and he would go on to be called the most powerful Demon King in history.

There was an inn with an urban legend among adventurers.  &quot;The Inn that won't let you die if you stay there.&quot;

Loretta arrives at the inn as part of her quest.  What is the secret of the &quot;Deathless Inn?&quot;

&quot;Save Point.&quot;

It was an inn ran by an maxed out adventurer with the ability to create &quot;Save Points&quot; who came from another world.  He retired from being an adventurer and decided to run an inn, while training newbie adventurers.  Loretta, who needs to become strong, will be trained by the innkeeper, Alexander.

If you die, don't worry about it, just hit load!


[b]TL;DR[/b]:  
Isekai + RPG Save Points + POV of a Native instead of the OP Otherworlder
