[spoiler]Franz Hellman zostaje pojmany przez wrogą armię. Przesłuchuje go generał Wenzke, kt&oacute;ry aby wyciągnąć z niego informacje torturuje go i poniża. Czy Hellman poradzi sobie w ciężkich wojennych warunkach? Czy przeżyje?

Always-surrounded-by-friends Ryuunosuke and lone wolf Kagetora are leaders of opposing teams and they have a cat-and-dog relationship.

One day, they end up doing erotic things: &quot;This can't be. I'm sharing a secret with this guy.&quot; There are also plans to move far away, and things get complicated. As these two who cannot seem to grow up consider their friends, hometown, family and their feelings for each other, they take their first clumsy steps into love.

This volume also contains the story of adult love between a younger manga artist and his Do-M editor! Even though his body was held captive &quot;for the sake of producing ero manga&quot;, the manga artist discovers a pleasure switch that even he didn't know about&hellip;

With a status of a slave, Azrael has served a noble&rsquo;s whipping child. In this misery, one mysterious man comes into her life.

&ldquo;Why are you living a life like this?&rdquo;
&ldquo;Do you know me?&rdquo;

In the three years of her life she&rsquo;s forgotten, the one who gave her a name was the Wizard of the Horizon, Rhema Resht.  His kindness yet lacking something, caught her attention. She wanted him to be as happy as she was.

&ldquo;The more you get to know me, misfortune will come.&rdquo;
&ldquo;I promise I won&rsquo;t be miserable, Rhema. So, please teach me magic.&rdquo;

